{"tid":1228074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB 我屌你老母","createTime":"2019-06-15T16:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T15:51:52.000Z","uid":122379,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"74695247e9641a2c388370249ee755e7c313f215","tid":1228074,"uid":122379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:18:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z1TuuTg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1TuuTg.png&h=9f6c8974&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係金鐘太古廣場危站近5個鐘，最後死埋<br />\nTVB 竟然報都冇報<br />\n網站又冇新聞<br />\n晚間新聞又係冇報<br />\n寧願報道日本有幾百隻馬食禁藥畀人停賽<br />\n我屌你老味關我撚事咩<br />\n宜家係死左人呀<br />\n你地咁撚樣做完全係侮辱埋有訴求嗰個義士<br />\n選擇性報道  完全冇新聞操守及職業道德<br />\n唔知以為睇緊中央電視台新聞聯播<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">TVB  我屌你老母  執柒左佢啦</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"86adf700ebe1a61eb9c9cea39bb90a03bd9bbace","tid":1228074,"uid":335251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T15:51:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}